---
title: Courgette and Pork Chilli with cannellini beans and leek
description: A variation on a traditional chilli con carne, this hearty stew uses courgette and leek for added taste and texture—and some added good-for-you nutrients too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF230112_R02_W10_IE_IECQP0162-2_Main_high-6ddb7e38.jpg
